      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and drives, but has some mechanical issues that may require attention in the near term. The exterior shows visible wear including scratches, minor dents, and some fading. The interior has noticeable wear on seats and surfaces. Suitable for a buyer willing to put some work into it.",
